'''''Ugly Truth''''' was a [[Starship/Legends|spacecraft]] located on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] during the time of the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. The spacecraft, formerly owned by [[Hasville Terson|Hasville]] and [[Adray Terson]], was disguised as a covered [[Landspeeder/Legends|landspeeder]]. [[Viqi Shesh]] attempted to escape the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] on it, but was stopped by members of [[Wraith Squadron]], who escaped on the ship instead, traveling in it to [[Borleias/Legends|Borleias]] with the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]].<ref name="CSWE">{{CSWECite|III|276|''Ugly Truth''}}</ref>

